articles.author: AP
articles.title: Five Americans 'are finally coming home' after Iran imprisonment, says Joe Biden - Hindustan Times
articles.description: In a statement, Biden thanked the governments of Qatar, Oman, Switzerland and South Korea for their help securing the Americans' release. | World News
articles.content:
US President Joe Biden said on Monday that five U.S. citizens who were detained in Iran "are finally coming home" after the two countries reached a deal for their release.
